1. Create a javascript class, Product
2. The class should set the name of the product, the quantity and the unit price during
instantiation
3. Create a method in the class which when called will display the ff

Name of Product: The name of product goes here
Quantity: the quantity goes here
Price: the price goes here

4. Add a method to the class that displays a form with the following fields
Name of Product, Quantity and Price and a submit button

5. Apply some CSS to make your work neat and nice